column5: 1st drift small shaker....2nd drift brownie! Definitely was mad at me on the first pic    An action shot from the day...feeeeesh on!   Nice to see a lot of these little guys around        Then came the evening bite...heres the hog right at sunset      Tight lines!
awesome, nice shots of the brown.  last fish is a tank
I'm digging the action shot, really loving that rock sticking out.  Oh, and turn on your phone.
Looks like a great day!  Man the tribs have been awesome for you guys...
You bugger! Here I am on the north shore of lake superior and I couldn't bring my combo.  Awesome fish!!
Kush-Brother:  Sweet brown--keep the pics comin man!!!
I love steelhead, but love getting browns like the one you got even more!  Great job
